Package: gaitkit
Type: Package
Title: Universal Gait Event Detection Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Frederic", "Fer",
    email = "frederic.fer@univ-poitiers.fr",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: Detect heel-strike and toe-off events from motion capture data
    using 10 validated methods (BIKE, Zeni, OConnor, Hreljac, Mickelborough,
    Ghoussayni, Vancanneyt, DGEI, IntellEvent, DeepEvent). Includes ensemble
    voting, gait cycle extraction, and publication-ready visualisation.
    C-accelerated Python backend accessed through 'reticulate'.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/fferlab/gaitkit
BugReports: https://github.com/fferlab/gaitkit/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    reticulate (>= 1.28)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
